sitions. More than 90% of &quot;Fortune 500&quot; enterprises are our customers, and currently over 100 Human Resource Services Providers are our advertisement customers and the sponsors.\r\n\r\n\u8054\u7cfb\u6211\u4eec\uff1a\r\n\r\nHR\u7ba1\u7406\u4e16\u754c\u5e02\u573a\u90e8\r\n\u7535\u3000\u8bdd\uff1a021-58215127\uff0c58215197\r\n\u4f20\u3000\u771f\uff1a021-58218663\r\n\u5730\u3000\u5740\uff1a\u4e0a\u6d77\u5e02\u6d66\u4e1c\u6843\u6797\u8def18\u53f7\u73af\u7403\u5e7f\u573aB\u5ea72203\u30012508\u5ba4\r\n\u90ae\u3000\u7f16\uff1a200135", "imagename": "14d0dd0539cb4c9e9b1fbca9f3b12bab.gif", "infoid": 17531, "category": "technology_web2", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["\u641c\u7d22", "\u641c\u7d22\u5f15\u64ce"]}]